track_notes: To reach the parking your car must have hight wheels to drive on the forest road! There is no path at the end for the summit but it is easy to found the way if wx is clear

I think is is a bit hard to climb there (hi hi)! In fact there is a part of the track that was icy; and then it was very difficullt to progress. The is no path, you must found your own way, witch is evident if you can see the summit clearly.
